{"output":{"publishTime":"2019-11-1","parent":"0","flag":"addNews","classids":"48,0,0","author":null,"hashcode":"1889609496","count":"0","title":"关于开展研究生海外联合培养基地建设项目申报工作的通知","picture":null,"content":"<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); white-space: normal; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 32px;\"><font face=\"宋体\">各位老师：<\/font><\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: SimSun, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">为进一步拓宽学生海外联合培养渠道，提升研究生教育国际化水平，提高研究生人才培养质量，学校决定开展<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">2019<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">年研究生海外联合培养基地建设项目的申报工作，现将相关事项通知如下：<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: SimSun, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">一、申报要求<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: SimSun, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">研究生海外联合培养基地合作单位应为国际高水平学术机构，并已与我校签订研究生联合培养协议（经<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\">教育部<\/strong>备案），能够在研究生培养及相关领域与我校深度合作，进行双学位联合培养（即学生毕业时可同时向双方学校申请对应学位）。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: SimSun, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">二、经费资助<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: SimSun, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">学校对立项的建设项目给予经费资助，学校、学院、学科共同投入，学校资助经费支出范围包括：<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: SimSun, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">（一）基地建设费用<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: SimSun, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">1.<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">我校与合作单位双方教师为开展深入合作的互派费用；<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: SimSun, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">2.<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">合作单位教师来我校开设联合培养课程的相关费用。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: SimSun, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">（二）联合培养费用<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: SimSun, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">不低于项目总经费的<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">70%<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">，用于支付联合培养研究生的国外生活费用（指学校国际化培养项目资助范围以外的费用），生活费的资助标准参照《浙江工业大学研究生国际化培养专项项目管理办法》。申请联合培养费用应具备以下条件：<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: SimSun, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">1.<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">派遣研究生的培养模式原则上为双学位联合培养；<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\"><\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: SimSun, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">2.<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">派遣研究生回国后需参加我校的论文送审及答辩环节后方能授予学位。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: SimSun, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">三、项目申报、立项程序<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: SimSun, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">1.<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">各学院组织申报。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: SimSun, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">申报人员填写《浙江工业大学研究生海外联合培养基地建设项目申请表》（附件<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">1<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">）及《浙江工业大学研究生海外联合培养基地建设项目申报汇总表》（附件<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">2<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">）并提供研究生联合培养协议，签字盖章后将书面稿（一式<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">3<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">份）、电子稿在<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">2019<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">年<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">11<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">月<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">8<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">日前交到学院办公室<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">余老师处<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline: none;\">(联系电话：<\/a><\/span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline: none;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">88320949<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">，<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">Email<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">：<\/span><\/a><a href=\"mailto:jxk@zjut.edu.cn\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\"><\/a><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline: none;\"><\/a><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline: none;\"><\/a><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: windowtext; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\"><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline: none;\"><\/a><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline: none;\"><\/a>yhljojo@zjut.edu.cn<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">）。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: SimSun, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">2.<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">研究生院组织评审。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: SimSun, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">3.<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">主管校长审批，立项发文。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: SimSun, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">四、其他事项<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: SimSun, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">联合培养的研究生海外培养结束回国后，提交在外交流或学习心得及相关成果，根据《浙江工业大学研究生国际化培养专项项目管理办法》中短期访学研究生的要求提交相关成果等材料。<\/span><\/p><p><br/><\/p><p style=\"line-height: 16px;\"><img style=\"vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 2px;\" src=\"/../ueditor/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_doc.gif\"/><a style=\"font-size:12px; color:#0066cc;\" href=\"/ueditor/jsp/upload/file/20191101/1572591168484090240.doc\" title=\"附件1：浙江工业大学研究生海外联合培养基地建设项目申请表.doc\">附件1：浙江工业大学研究生海外联合培养基地建设项目申请表.doc<\/a><\/p><p style=\"line-height: 16px;\"><img style=\"vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 2px;\" src=\"/../ueditor/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_xls.gif\"/><a style=\"font-size:12px; color:#0066cc;\" href=\"/ueditor/jsp/upload/file/20191101/1572591178031014692.xls\" title=\"附件2：浙江工业大学研究生海外联合培养基地建设项目申报汇总表.xls\">附件2：浙江工业大学研究生海外联合培养基地建设项目申报汇总表.xls<\/a><\/p><p><br/><\/p>","secondtitle":null,"classid":"48","redtitle":"否","webtype":"内外网","istop":"否","grandparent":"0","publisher":"yxyyb","department":null,"titleurl":null}}